{"id":9417,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">今年，《炎黄春秋》杂志单本价格提高为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">元，售价提高并未影响杂志发行量。相反，在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">全国报刊订数大幅下落的形势下，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《炎黄春秋》今年的发行量强势增</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">长了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">15%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，从而进入“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2013</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中国邮政发行报刊百强排行榜”的“期刊</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">强”中的前</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">名。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“手机报”订阅户达</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=EN-US>327</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">万。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">ipad</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">版和</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">iphone</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">版海外订阅已达北美、欧洲、日本、东南亚和港台等地区。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">正如</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《炎黄春秋》的作者所说，能够在国内数万种报刊中逆势增长，说明《炎黄春秋》与众不同。尽管《炎黄春秋》装帧简单，与国内其它期刊相比，甚至简陋，但并不影响读者对它的喜爱。《炎黄春秋》的发行量逆势增</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">长的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">15%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这个现象，值得研究。一些读者来信指出，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《炎黄春秋》所刊登的许多文章敢于直面史实，且有深入剖析，引人深思。《炎黄春秋》能够从历史角度解析当前中国政治体制改革，对推动政体改革，少走弯路，不无裨益。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《炎黄春秋》能够连续</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">年保持发行量持续增长的势头，首先要感谢广大读者对《炎黄春秋》的信任和支持。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">要感谢</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《炎黄春秋》</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的作者和各界朋友的帮助，是你们的智慧吸引了读者。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT size=3>《炎黄春秋》的全体工作人员将一如既往，为办好《炎黄春秋》尽心竭力，将这本外表普通的杂志办出不普通的风采。</FONT></SPAN></P>","title":"2014年《炎黄春秋》发行量强势增长","time":1393090785000}